methods.name: uninitializedRead
methods.comment:
An attempt has been made to read uninitialized memory at the 
 specified address.

params.name: address
params.comment: uninitialized storage address (memory, register or unique)

return.comment: true if data should be treated as initialized

methods.name: unknownAddress
methods.comment: Unable to translate the specified address

params.name: address
params.comment: address which failed to be translated

params.name: write
params.comment: true if memory operation was a write vs. read
